title: Packers hold off pass-happy Chargers for 27-20 win
text:
> Sports Packers hold off pass-happy Chargers for 27-20 win Green Bay Packers' Damarious Randall (23) celebrates after breaking up a pass intended for San Diego Chargers' Danny Woodhead on the final play of an NFL football game Sunday, Oct. 18, 2015, in Green Bay, Wis. The Packers won the game 27-20. (AP Photo/Jeffrey Phelps)
